Abstract: The couple are married in Princeton, N.J.
Snippet: The couple are married in Princeton, N.J.
LeadParagraph: Petra Elliott Kann and Thomas Patrick Weir were married Saturday at Miller Chapel at the Princeton Theological Seminary in Princeton, N.J. The Rev. David C. Mertz, a United Methodist minister, led the ceremony with his wife, the Rev. Dr. Nancy J. Duff, a Presbyterian minister, taking part.
